sequenceDiagram
    participant RSS as RSS Feed
    participant RF as RSS Fetcher
    participant HC as HTML Cleaner
    participant GCS as GCS Storage
    participant RI as RAG Ingester
    participant RC as RAG Corpus
    participant VS as Vector Search
    
    RSS->>RF: Fetch RSS XML
    RF->>RF: Parse RSS Items
    RF->>RF: Detect New Items
    RF->>GCS: Save Raw XML
    
    loop For Each New Item
        RF->>RF: Fetch HTML Content
        RF->>GCS: Save Raw HTML
        RF->>HC: Clean HTML
        HC->>HC: Remove Scripts/Styles
        HC->>HC: Extract Article Content
        HC->>HC: Prepend Metadata
        HC->>GCS: Save Cleaned Text
        
        GCS->>RI: Reference GCS URI
        RI->>RC: Import File (LRO)
        RC->>RC: Chunk Text (768 words, 128 overlap)
        RC->>RC: Generate Embeddings
        RC-->>RI: Import Complete
        
        HC->>VS: Generate Embedding
        VS->>VS: Upsert Vector
    end

